Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.79,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:40.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:51.27,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:57.57,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:03.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:11.27,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.35,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Two years have passed since the great war at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:23.63,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats regrouped at their promised meeting place, the Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.77,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Now, after setting off for\Ntheir next destination; The New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.56,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,they have finally made it to Fishman Island, located ten thousand meters under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:35.86,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But there they find that the New Fishman Pirates\Nare planning to overthrow the Ryuuguu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.86,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and Vander Decken has been stalking the Mermaid Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:44.24,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Crew find themselves drawn into these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:50.28,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy makes his way toward the Sea Forest with Shirahoshi, Vander Decken blocks his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:54.62,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you, I presume!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.02,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.22,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:07.82,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,This is between me and my beloved Shirahoshi.  Why must you get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.37,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Shark forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:26.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Zoro's group remain in Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:31.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,He is locked in a fierce battle with Hody, the leader of the New Fishman Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:36.99,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, you inferior scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.71,Thoughts,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.84,Main,Underlings,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!  Boss!  Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:28.09,Main,Underlings,0000,0000,0000,,How can a human move faster than\Na fishman in the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.63,Main,Underlings,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.23,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,My air's run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.87,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  How dare he do that to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.07,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.89,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a human!  He can't breathe underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.49,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that swordsman get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.53,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone take your Energy Steroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:12.18,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,What a nuisance they are!\NExterminate everyone in the Neptune Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.97,Thoughts,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:26.03,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?  Such an unnatural aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.61,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.74,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?  He isn't coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:43.11,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.\NMy strength is completely drained and it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.52,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.02,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Kill 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:05.02,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,You can only manage to defend yourself, huh?  Just give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.49,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of air, ain't ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.45,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.08,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting desperate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.33,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for you!  Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.02,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,That coward would never fight me one on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.43,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.  If they're gonna fight like that then we'll massacre everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.25,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.95,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,The palace will be completely flooded soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.58,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,You should grab on to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.61,Thoughts,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking out our best soldiers so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:57.81,Thoughts,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,They must be using some sort of sinister power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:01.21,Thoughts,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought,\NI must get all the soldiers out of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:05.08,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Use this to make sure you have air -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.59,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.19,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto my body tightly -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.01,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.35,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,We can't delay, we must go now -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.44,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!  Over here!  Grab hold of the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.89,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my injured back will hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:38.03,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, soldiers!\NWe're gonna carve a path out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.74,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stay and fight.  Flee the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.88,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.03,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.58,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune's doing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.75,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.91,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!  Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.28,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Men, go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.29,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.94,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Ride the current as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:28.15,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they're running away without fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.59,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Hody!  Quickly, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:37.09,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of the castle!  Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.22,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Go through the connecting channel, all the way to the mainland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.10,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man!\NGet it together!  I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.17,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Age can be so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:51.48,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move at all -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.86,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.20,Main,what's his bucket,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.74,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.08,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.25,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though this is the end for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.15,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.43,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.59,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,You've saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:26.71,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my frailty.\NI couldn't even move my neck -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:27.91,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:31.06,Main,what's his bucket,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God, Hoe helped him get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.58,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.68,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.46,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.12,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.81,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:16.30,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!  Hody caught His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:20.49,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Hody supposed to be incapacitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:24.84,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Right!  Let's go back!\NAt this rate, His Majesty's going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.16,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:34.67,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,You must go on without me,\Nand bring back Fukaboshi and his brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.29,Main,what's his bucket,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!  Obey the King's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.55,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.92,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Hody, is it okay to let them get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.32,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah it's fine, let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:54.30,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What can a bunch of warriors who'd abandon their king do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:58.73,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly,\Ntie up this foolish king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.53,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.45,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.07,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't let you get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.97,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.34,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?  Probably someone's skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.58,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.39,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, were the Straw Hat Pirates here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.85,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:34.04,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,The staff at this store saw them, but after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.98,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune-sama invited\NStraw Hat Luffy and four others to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:42.52,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,They must be the ones inside of the palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.77,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Most certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.67,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,So they're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:49.24,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened to the two\Nwho were at Coral Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.29,Main,Ryuuboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been able to\Nestablish contact with them -mi re do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:58.21,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  That's not a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.53,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Akkamanbo!  Fuuri, fuuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:05.57,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I think something must have happened.  Shouldn't we go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.43,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.23,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi!  Prince Fukaboshi, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.06,Main,Ryuuboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.43,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fukaboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.88,Main,Telephone,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, we've got a major problem over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.23,Main,Telephone,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Waterwheel District.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.11,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,The Waterwheel District?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:22.01,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Some people from the Fishman District came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.83,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,and started attacking the town.  Queen Otohime{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.24,Main,Underling,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have gone and done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.96,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Mother?!  Hey!  Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.10,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the Waterwheel District!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:43.98,Main,Anmonaitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.97,Main,Muhhi,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.74,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're headed for the Waterwheel District.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.21,Main,Muh,0000,0000,0000,,That Dosun... Doesn't he know that\Nit's too early to start the attack -hhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:01.19,Main,Muh,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point unless\Nwe all do it at the same time -hhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.71,Main,Muh,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, we'll just start over here, then -hhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.11,Main,Muh,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.99,Main,Muh,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moment we've been waiting for -hhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.30,Main,Muh,0000,0000,0000,,Go wild and plunder to your heart's content -hhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.87,Main,Fishmen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.39,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,This place is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.15,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Sea Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:47.40,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I've always wanted to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:52.82,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly indebted to you, Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.38,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can rest and recuperate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:04.09,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid.... Mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.63,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.38,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.05,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!  Franky's there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:16.23,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franky!  So this is where you've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.64,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.81,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:26.73,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you didn't bring a pinup girl with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.99,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce ya.  This is Wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:39.29,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Wimp, huh?\NSounds like you need to get your act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:44.00,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sorry for troubling you.  My name is Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.94,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, are you the only one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.80,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Robin was here too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.70,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,but then she went off in search of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:56.27,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,She went into that huge coral forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.24,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.06,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,{I completely forgot his spelling in English}Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.83,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:28.21,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're quite a bit stronger.  I can see the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.88,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you weren't down here,\Nso I didn't think I'd be able to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:35.69,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NDidn't you get my message to meet me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:38.64,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NI don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.81,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.98,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jinbe-sama,\Nit's certainly been quite a while since we last met.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:48.44,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for failing to keep in touch with you,\NPrincess Shirahoshi-sam{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.36,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.91,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess Shirahoshi!  Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:59.37,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Franky!  I wanna bring\NHachi and Sanji down, so give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:01.97,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.43,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,If it ain't the octopus guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.22,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.50,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hachi!  What!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:13.28,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Where did those injuries come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.09,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,\Nwhy are you on Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:19.51,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you captured along with Arlong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.52,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe-san, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.05,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!  Sanji's next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.95,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.40,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.41,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:47.67,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Before you, I am like an artist with no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:54.65,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,For you see, there is no brush\Nthat could properly capture your radiance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:55.51,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:18:01.05,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,That's... his normal reaction\Nin the presence of women!  He's all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:05.35,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,My canvas could never reflect the beauty\Nthat you possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.90,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!  Hooray!\NSanji's returned to his normal strange self!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.11,Main,Den,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is loud over there... I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:17.07,Main,Den,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Princess Shirahoshi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:21.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Who're you?!  Why are you on the Sunny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He's Den-chan, the younger brother of Tom,\Nmy carpentry master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.83,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He's fixing the ship's coating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.08,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He's the master who's going to\Ncoat your younger brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.76,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's close enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:46.31,Main,Jimbei,0000,0000,0000,,But Princess Shirahoshi-sama,\NI understand why you wanted to come here but{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.65,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.07,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Even after the beating I gave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,How many times has it been now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He's really persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:07.95,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, now!\NWhy'd you bring the Princess here, Luffy-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:11.37,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!  I'm here, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:12.65,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.96,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:25.14,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the tomb she was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:32.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,She's really been going at it for a long time, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.52,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,This is where her mother, Queen Otohime, is resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:44.29,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken's started his obstinate courtship...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.60,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,right after the Queen passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.94,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this,\Nthe Princess couldn't even attend her mother's funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.67,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,and she's spent ten years in Koukaku Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:10.17,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,She must have so many things she wants to tell her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.11,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.61,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!  Caimie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.61,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chin, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:29.17,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's standing next to Luffy-chin is Boss Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.92,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.  Princess Shirahoshi is there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.63,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!  Has the banquet started yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:47.89,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-swaaaaaaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.89,Secondary,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.77,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Hacchin!  What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.05,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Caimie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:58.81,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?  Hody did such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:20:59.70,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:05.01,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the situation\Nat Ryuuguu Palace is so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.07,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened to Zoro and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.79,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:11.04,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd go back after we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.11,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:18.71,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that my father could be captured like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.96,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:31.92,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to you to get into any trouble,\Nthat's why I left a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.81,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that you've already been caught up in our affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:40.66,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It is important for us to hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.53,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,but when I met you two years ago the circumstances were different,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.40,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn't tell you this story at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:58.17,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to offer you my most profound gratitude for stopping Arlong's crew in East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:02.25,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.68,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:06.66,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'd like to give my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:10.11,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, I must apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:13.34,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:20.91,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The one who set Arlong loose on East Blue eleven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:23.79,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:11.05,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe tells the crew about his shocking past,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.71,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and revives painful memories of Arlong for Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.83,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The relationship between\NJinbe and the crew grows tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:22.67,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe reveals the truth about two great people...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:25.96,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,who attempted to fix the tragic history between humans and fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.38,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrected Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:30.93,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the Fishman Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.61,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the Pirate King!
